<section id="neutron-welcome-screen">
	<h1>Hello Neutron!</h1>

	<p>Welcome to <a href="https://github.com/vebersol/neutron/">Neutron</a> Atomic Design Tool. These pages are automatically generated as a static site.</p>

	<h2>How to use Neutron?</h2>

	<p>To use <strong>Neutron</strong> is quite simple. At the left/right corner you may see a button, the <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" class="neutron-svg-inline"><use class="neutron-svg-icon" xlink:href="#neutron-logo"></use></svg> button. To activate <strong>Neutron</strong> Navigation, you just need to press the key <strong>n</strong> or click/touch on this button.</p>

	<p>The <strong>Neutron</strong> navigation bar consists in:</p>

	<ul>
		<li>
			<svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" class="neutron-svg-inline">
				<use class="neutron-svg-icon" xlink:href="#neutron-search"></use>
			</svg>
			Search Button - opens the search input and find your desired pattern
		</li>
		<li>
			<svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" class="neutron-svg-inline">
				<use class="neutron-svg-icon" xlink:href="#neutron-code-frame"></use>
			</svg>
			Code Frame Button - opens a frame below containing your HTML and Handlebars markup, including the pattern documentation. It also shows the dependencies and reverse dependencies list.
		</li>
		<li>
			<svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" class="neutron-svg-inline">
				<use class="neutron-svg-icon" xlink:href="#neutron-qr-code"></use>
			</svg>
			QR Code Button - opens a lightbox with QR Code to easily load it in your mobile device.
		</li>
		<li>
			<svg viewBox="0 0 1792 1792" class="neutron-svg-inline">
				<use class="neutron-svg-icon" xlink:href="#neutron-settings"></use>
			</svg>
			Settings Button - opens a lightbox with basic information and settings.
		</li>
		<li>Main menu including all patterns: Atoms, Molecules, Organisms, Templates, Pages</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>Shortcuts</h2>

	<table>
		<thead>
			<tr>
				<th>Key</th>
				<th>Description</th>
			</tr>
		</thead>
		<tbody>
			<tr>
				<td><strong>n</strong></td>
				<td>Show <strong>Neutron</strong> navigation bar</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td><strong>f</strong></td>
				<td>Find patterns</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td><strong>c</strong></td>
				<td>Toggle code frame (when in a pattern)</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td><strong>q</strong></td>
				<td>Toggle QR Code window</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td><strong>s</strong></td>
				<td>Toggle settings window</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td><strong>m</strong></td>
				<td>Focus first menu item to enable keyboard navigation</td>
			</tr>
		</tbody>
	</table>

	<h2>Read More</h2>

	<p>To read more about <strong>Neutron</strong>, please check our <a href="https://github.com/vebersol/neutron/blob/master/README.md">README</a>.</p>

	<p><em><strong>Neutron</strong> is attached by default in all generated pages as a standalone script, it means you must have Javascript enabled by default.</em></p>
